{"tid":831280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普要油國組織現在就降價 油價應聲下挫","createTime":"2018-09-21T19:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T04:27:31.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5fdbf6c6a8152cbb81789ab9f979e084b9d50ec5","tid":831280,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T19:46:06.000Z","msg":"2018-09-21 06:43中央社 紐約20日綜合外電報導<br />\n<br />\n世界油價本週稍早測試每桶80美元價位後，美國總統川普今天推文批評石油輸出國家組織（OPEC），要這些產油國「現在就降價」，油價果然應聲下跌。<br />\n<br />\n在紐約商品交易所，美國市場基準商品西德州中級原油期貨價格下跌32美分，收在每桶70.80美元。<br />\n<br />\n倫敦市場北海布倫特原油下跌70美分，收在78.70美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6811/3379521\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6811%2F3379521&d=%2FwY0s8x9hsXdpF5SfaepXNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e615643e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6811/3379521</a>"},{"pid":"e86c0462fb1b93be6d709bc623d4cef6c8e3a70f","tid":831280,"uid":208722,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T20:00:23.000Z","msg":"中國買俄佬啲油幾錢？"},{"pid":"e9ddcd66d50e202cc34d0f9d60e5451e57bd6cda","tid":831280,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T20:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc58a904cee8cda04b30142c1d7a5c24a4e46d1","tid":831280,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T22:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> shell 17.19 / L"},{"pid":"8065677ec4b0c8d504044c99be2031f04cdbbae6","tid":831280,"uid":134161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T23:05:30.000Z","msg":"特首幾時出出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c788078acdf74aabe1bd685a9c982fc465811b23","tid":831280,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21